{"tid":1965554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衛生署宣布星期六起檢疫人士在檢疫中心十日後可以回家自行隔離","createTime":"2020-04-09T14:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T14:16:07.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"48595ff6739b0418e2b24c76379a147363a0ae80","tid":1965554,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:13:42.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情肆虐，衞生署衞生防護中心今日宣布，因應檢疫中心的容量情況，有需要時可安排受檢疫人士在入住檢疫中心 10 天後，於餘下 4 天返回家居繼續檢疫，將會在 4 月 11 日（星期六）起逐步於各檢疫中心實行，以確保有足夠檢疫設施。檢疫人士離開檢疫中心前，會戴上電子手環，以確保他們遵守家居檢疫的要求。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心指，一直檢視各個檢疫中心的使用情況和需求，鑒於疫情發展迅速，而密切接觸者數目亦維持在較高水平，預期對檢疫設施的需求將有增無減。<br />\n<br />\n中心又強調，所有於檢疫中心接受檢疫的人士均沒有病徵，新措施推行後，檢疫人士於離開中心前須進行病毒測試。若檢測結果呈陰性，並經過醫護人員的評估其健康狀況及其他相關因素，認為適合於餘下四天在家中繼續檢疫，才會實行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E8%B5%B7%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E4%BD%8F%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E7%87%9F-10-%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%8C-%E9%A4%98%E4%B8%8B-4-%E6%97%A5%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25BD%258F%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E7%2587%259F-10-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E9%25A4%2598%25E4%25B8%258B-4-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=2610106c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25AD%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E4%25BD%258F%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2%25E7%2587%259F-10-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E9%25A4%2598%25E4%25B8%258B-4-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%2F&h=35869f98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%91%A8%E5%85%AD%E8%B5%B7%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E4%BD%8F%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2%E7%87%9F-10-%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%8C-%E9%A4%98%E4%B8%8B-4-%E6%97%A5%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB/</a>"},{"pid":"6166b84c93ee4719d48e470a2a4f82a3ed6a9c61","tid":1965554,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}